{
  "stem": "8892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And when we went back to that shower, by that time, you already heard enough stories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And you were aware that this is it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You're not going to come out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And when you did come out, there was a bigger shock that you're really alive-- and they just showered you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they give us some other junk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we were assigned to C Lager.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] Auschwitz-- actually, our function was-- that time, it was getting up, 5 o'clock, raus.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They would keep us outside-- rain, shine, and cool morning-- three, four hours.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And every day, they count us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They were very good of keeping records, the German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They had to count us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "If one was missing out of line-- like I told you, formation of five-- and one may be sick, or, or left in a barrack, or really escaped, or something, or died, you would be punished, a whole barrack.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we would be outside for hours and hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And then we learned what Auschwitz like.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we saw the barbed wires, you know, electrical.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We even witnessed two girls get electrocuted because they see their cousins, or somebody, relation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "They see that they're just marching into the other camp through the wires.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And they're not even thinking, and they're running like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "[POINTS] And in that second, they were electrocuted.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
